beer.beer_description: Space Dust is out of this world, with 62 IBU, and 8.2% ABV. This citrus-forward IPA balances bitterness with a sweetness of hop flavors. Grapefruit, mango, and orange aromas with a medium body and a dry finish. (p.s. It's a hop, not an artichoke!)
